This is a list of biological viruses. See also Comparison of computer viruses
This is an alphabetical list of biological virus species. It includes all species of virus listed by the ICTV 2015 report 1.
Excluded are other ranks of virus, viroids and prions. Also excluded are more recently discovered viruses such as Bourbon Virus, common names and obsolete names for viruses.
For a list of virus genera, see List of genera of viruses.
For a list of virus families and subfamilies, see List of virus families and subfamilies.
For a taxonomic list, see Taxonomic list of viruses.
